item.title: Home
item.description:
In the interest of keeping spoiler stuff separated inside Discord.
Both Weyway's pages are separated into different projects on Github.
However, you can access both below.
Spoiler warning! If you are not fond of spoilers and have not enabled that role on discord, beware navigating to the Raids and Dungeons page.
This page will contain information related to content in-game that might be current (e.g. MSQ trials)
You've been warned!
